# Reproduces the segfault Vlad observed on 2026-04-23: a normal chat turn
# crashes the agent runner during EventQueue.deinit on .done. Drives zag
# via the mock provider so the reproducer is offline + deterministic.

spawn ./zig-out/bin/zag
wait_text /Welcome to zag/
send "hello" <Enter>
wait_exit
snapshot final
